<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蚯蚓小组站在柳树溪公墓的入口处。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雨刚停。最后的水滴从树枝上落下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰雾在傍晚的空气中飘过，落在坟墓上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦。”卢克说，“好吓人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”凯蒂说，“就像一部恐怖电影！哇哈哈！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们为什么不白天来？”阿杰问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为，”艾米丽说，“白天我们可能会遇到另一个寻宝小组。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果没有其它问题，我们就忙起来吧。”凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得检查所有的老坟墓。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米丽看了看阿杰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“既然你不识字，就坐在这张长椅上等着吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿杰咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就我一个人吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你当我们的卫兵。”卢克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果有什么不对劲的，就喊我们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇哈哈！”凯蒂又说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有这个，拿好购物袋。”艾米丽说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等。”阿杰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但三个蚯蚓小组成员在雾中消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿杰颤抖着坐在长椅上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把购物袋放在腿上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他听着声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个是1952年的。”那是艾米丽。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个是1943年的。”那是卢克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“1917年。”那是凯蒂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>声音越来越远。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，一切都静止了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿杰坐着的长椅旁边，有一块大理石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿杰把头向后仰，抬头向上看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一位阴沉的女士大理石像站在那个四方的大理石顶上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它直视着阿杰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别管我。”阿杰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他移到长椅的另一端。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他晃了晃腿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他吹了几声口哨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他慢慢地抬起头来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那位大理石女士正盯着他的眼睛看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿杰颤抖着，移开了目光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们为什么让我一个人呆着？”他想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是蚯蚓小组的成员啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他听到一个声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿杰！”那个声音叫道，“阿杰！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿杰！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁在那儿？”他低声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿杰！在这里！把购物袋拿过来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿杰跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“姐姐！”他大喊道，沿着小路跑进雾中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在墓地边上一片黑黑的松树林附近发现了蚯蚓小组。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们聚在一块旧墓碑四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个是1859年的。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿杰盯着石头看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在找到了，我们该怎么办？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把它放进我们购物袋里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈！”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，你真傻。”艾米丽对她弟弟说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们用蜡笔拓印。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们最好快点儿。”卢克说，“太阳快落山了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂展开了纸。“卢克和阿杰，抓住上面。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她向艾米丽伸出手去。“把蜡笔给我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂用蜡笔涂了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>墓碑上的文字开始出现：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260948</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米丽</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔治•沃森 亲爱的</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿杰回头看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你听到了吗？”他低声说，“树上有东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蚯蚓小组仔细地听着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我什么也没听到。”艾米丽说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也没听到。”凯蒂说。她又涂了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米丽</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔治•沃森 亲爱的妻子</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>死亡</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>1859年，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我听到了！”艾米丽说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有东西在那里动！”凯蒂抬头看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它在笑！”艾米丽说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，它在哭！”卢克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是大理石女士！”阿杰尖叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁？”蚯蚓小组大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别管了！”阿杰喊道，“我们走吧，姐姐！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得弄完！”卢克说，“我们需要日期！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂最后一次涂了一下蜡笔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米丽</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>334002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔治•沃森亲爱的妻子</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>334003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>死亡</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>86</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>1859年4月29日</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>87</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了！”凯蒂喊道，“我们走吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>88</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蚯蚓小组跌跌撞撞地在潮湿的草地上跑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>89</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>348003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>351253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“购物袋！”阿杰喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>90</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>351254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>354757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米丽跑回去，抱起了购物袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>91</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>354758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>357927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等我！”她尖叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>92</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>357928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>361902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙卷风小组从松树林中跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>93</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>361903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>366657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们哈哈大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>